Novice Panel Missions

■Perform a limit break 3 times on a realized piece of second 5★ armor and enhance it to max
Strategy Tip:
• Second 5★ armor are those with an initial rarity of 5★ and an initial CP of 90.
• They can be obtained by trading in twenty guard tokens at the guard token exchange.
*The guard tokens, book of Refuge's mysteries, and Refuge's adamantine ingots needed to clear this mission can be obtained by clearing the mission "Clear Act 1, Ch. 1, 'Primus Island.'"
